  "remarks": "The Center for Military Sports Training and patriotic education of youth “WARRIOR” is a state-led youth organisation established in the Russian Federation to develop patriotic and military education. It is supported by the President of the Russian Federation, who instructed the WARRIOR Center to work in close relationship with participants in Russia’s war of aggression against Ukraine. The WARRIOR Center is also conducting activities in the illegally occupied territories of Ukraine, through local branches.The WARRIOR Center is also conducting activities in the illegally occupied territories of Ukraine, through local branches.\nThe WARRIOR Center has also conducted several projects with the All-Russian public-state movement of children and youth “Movement of the First”, an entity listed by the Union.\nTherefore, the Center for Military Sports Training and patriotic education of youth “WARRIOR” is supporting or implementing actions or policies which undermine or threaten the territorial integrity, sovereignty and independence of Ukraine. It is also supporting, materially or financially, or benefitting from the Government of the Russian Federation, which is responsible for the annexation of Crimea and the destabilisation of Ukraine. The Center for Military Sports Training and patriotic education of youth “WARRIOR” is also associated with the All-Russian public-state movement of children and youth “Movement of the First”.",
